<table
  class="wrapper"
  cellpadding="0"
  cellspacing="0"
  role="presentation"
  width="100%"
>
  <tr>
    <td class="px-sm-16" align="center" bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
      <table
        class="container"
        cellpadding="0"
        cellspacing="0"
        role="presentation"
        width="600"
      >
        <tr>
          <td
            class="px-sm-8"
            align="left"
            bgcolor="#FFFFFF"
            style="padding: 0 24px"
          >
            <div
              class="spacer line-height-sm-0 py-sm-8"
              style="line-height: 24px"
            >
              &zwnj;
            </div>
            <table
              cellpadding="0"
              cellspacing="0"
              role="presentation"
              width="100%"
            >
              <tr>
                <td
                  class="col px-sm-16"
                  align="left"
                  width="100%"
                  style="padding: 0 64px"
                >
                  <div class="spacer" style="line-height: 48px">&zwnj;</div>
                  <table
                    cellpadding="0"
                    cellspacing="0"
                    role="presentation"
                    width="60%"
                  >
                    <tr>
                      <td class="col" align="left" width="100%">
                        <a href="https://biz.iwannabetter.com">
                          <img
                            src="https://iwannabetter.com/logo/logo1.png"
                            alt="Header Logo"
                            width="60%"
                          />
                        </a>
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                  </table>
                  <div class="spacer" style="line-height: 32px">&zwnj;</div>
                  <h2
                    style="
                      color: #888888;
                      font-size: 16px;
                      font-weight: 300;
                      line-height: 28px;
                      margin: 0 0 24px;
                    "
                  >
                    안녕하세요 방송콘텐츠진흥재단입니다.
                  </h2>
                  <p
                    style="
                      color: #888888;
                      font-size: 16px;
                      line-height: 24px;
                      margin: 0;
                    "
                  >
                    아래와 같이 로그인 링크를 보내드립니다.<br /><br />아래
                    링크를 클릭하여 계정에 로그인하세요. <br /><br />
                    아래의 이메일과 비밀번호를 사용해 주시고 반드시 비밀번호를
                    변경해주세요.
                    <br />
                    이메일: <%= email %> <br />
                    비밀번호: <%= password %>
                    <br />
                    <br />
                  </p>
                  <div class="spacer" style="line-height: 32px">&zwnj;</div>
                  <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation">
                    <tr>
                      <td
                        class="webfont hover-scale"
                        bgcolor="#32B38A"
                        style="
                          border-radius: 3px;
                          transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out 0s;
                          mso-padding-alt: 6px 32px 12px;
                        "
                      >
                        <a
                          href="<%= url %>"
                          style="
                            color: #ffffff;
                            display: inline-block;
                            font-size: 14px;
                            font-weight: 700;
                            padding: 12px 32px;
                            text-decoration: none;
                          "
                          >로그인</a
                        >
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                  </table>
                  <br />

                  <div class="spacer" style="line-height: 32px">&zwnj;</div>

                  <div class="spacer" style="line-height: 32px">&zwnj;</div>
                  <p
                    style="
                      color: #888888;
                      font-size: 16px;
                      line-height: 24px;
                      margin: 0;
                    "
                  >
                    Thanks, <br />
                    WANNAB Team
                  </p>
                </td>
              </tr>
            </table>
            <div
              class="spacer line-height-sm-0 py-sm-8"
              style="line-height: 24px"
            >
              &zwnj;
            </div>
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>
